{"tid":1569842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［大家入嚟討論一下］自己香港自己救！","createTime":"2019-09-14T18:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T19:05:39.000Z","uid":289457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"48e1cc0787c3717db99b9a5c8bd0d2c67a396cfa","tid":1569842,"uid":289457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:25:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">代post</span></span> <br />\n[size=<span style=\"color: red;\">4]&ldquo;打🐶！救人！&rdquo;</span>[/size=4]<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">點解仲未聽到現場有人嗌？<br />\n甘心見到班細路俾人拉？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n和理非嘅請你聽到有人嗌呢句就退後返後排充人數！<br />\n肯做嘅請你和應等大家都知有同路人！<br />\n喺有支援之前就好去馬！<br />\n想做但聽到唔夠人數嘅話咪當嗌下口號囉！<br />\n今日淘大俾狗cap住都可以救到人！<br />\n今日唔係奇蹟！有決心嗎？<br />\n<br />\n真。香港人真係無得再退！<br />\n已經過一千個手足被捕！<br />\n你願意冒呢個險嗎？<br />\n<br />\n有朋友今日喺淘大見好多呀叔呀嬸話一定要救人，唔可以縮！<br />\n但佢地又唔知應該點做！<br />\n但係勇武肯衝嘅會驚得自己一個<br />\n變相得自己一個會多一個送頭<br />\n所以點樣可以令佢地喺現場即時有個共識<br />\n甚至令和理非都知佢地會做乜？<br />\n<br />\n你唔嗌&rdquo;打🐶！救人&rdquo;就無人會做<br />\n係咪可以做多啲文宣令和理或者呀叔呀嬸都識走位？<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？不如交流下"},{"pid":"10daf249590bdbd895a7e49a764e52e869a382e3","tid":1569842,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4oZup8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4oZup8.jpg&h=22278f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=9f7e5f49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=aac17786\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"4d09782897e562b96d7a5a37debd85ce7575baa0","tid":1569842,"uid":289457,"